k #1 in the executor queue.\n*   **Purpose**: Allow agents to store and recall structured memory context.\n*   **Input**: Key-value pairs or text chunks.\n*   **Output**: Compressed references or targeted retrieval (aligning with TokenMaxxing goals to reduce context waste).\n\n## Verification & Testing\n1.  Verify the `overrides.env` file contains the correct structure.\n2.  Check `/tmp/workflow-executor.log` to confirm the 7 queued sessions are successfully processed without 401 or 503 errors.\n3.  Run `scripts/ai/aq-memory --help` to ensure the new script is executable and syntactically correct.", "output_file": ".agents/delegation/outputs/codex-20260513-162913-b07fzqxxxxxx.log", "pid": null, "status": "running", "created": "2026-05-13T23:29:13Z"}
