ompile ai-stack/mcp-servers/hybrid-coordinator/core/llm_client.py ai-stack/local-agents/agent_executor.py ai-stack/local-orchestrator/router.py\n\nReport: for each slice, show the exact diff you made and confirm py_compile passed.", "output_file": ".agents/delegation/outputs/codex-20260515-095945-0e1efrxxxxxx.log", "pid": 898811, "status": "running", "created": "2026-05-15T16:59:45Z"}
